            <title>[SOLR-15061] Fix NPE in SearchHandler when shards.info</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-15061</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This NPE happens in a specific case&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Short-circuited distributed request&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;With shards.info&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;With no QueryComponent (e.g. only spellcheck)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;One-liner fix in SearchHandler.handleRequestBody().&lt;/p&gt;</description>
